dev.marksman.enhancediterables

Interface NonEmptyIterable<A>

  • Type Parameters:
    A - the element type
    All Superinterfaces:
    EnhancedIterable<A>, java.lang.Iterable<A>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ImmutableNonEmptyFiniteIterable<A>, ImmutableNonEmptyIterable<A>, ImmutableNonEmptySet<A>, ImmutableNonEmptyVector<A>, NonEmptyFiniteIterable<A>, NonEmptySet<A>, NonEmptyVector<A>

    public interface NonEmptyIterable<A>
extends EnhancedIterable<A>
    An EnhancedIterable that is guaranteed to contain at least one element.

    May be infinite or finite.
